# Changelog

## [Unreleased]
### Added
### Changed
### Deprecated
### Removed
### Fixed
### Security

## [1.1.0] - 2020-03-14

### Added
    - Allow tiles rotation. 

## [1.0.1] - 2020-02-22

### Fixed
    - Do not move fullscreen client.

## [1.0.0] - 2020-02-22

### Added
    - Multihead support.

### Fixed
    - Some windows (e.g. firefox dialog) are created with a size of 1x1,
      the wm should rely on size hints (especially min size) to display
      properly the window. Apply the size hints at client creation time.
    - Allow the move of sticky windows.

## [0.9.2] - 2020-02-17

### Changed
    - Add style arguments.

### Fixed
    - Define all sticky window as floating.
    - Do not allow the move of sticky windows.

## [0.9.1] - 2020-02-11
    - Add BUGS files.
    - Do not use the -w option when calling killall mwmrc, that slows down the startup
    - Fullscreen support (refactor client mode and state)
    - rename MWM_COUNT to MWM_ATOM_COUNT

## [0.9.0] - 2020-02-11
    - Initial release.

